Curator's comments: Published: Pharaonen Und Fremde Catalogue (Vienna 1994): No.109
Exhibition history: Exhibited: 1994 7 Sep-26 Oct, Austria, Vienna, Museen der Stadt Wien, Pharanen und Fremde
Associated names: Named in inscription: Nubkheperre Intef VI
